	<tr>
		
			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				DO NOT try to kill Trumpy in the bar!  The bouncer will attack you and you will die.  Also don't attack him where guards can see you. Killing Trumpy, was easy, he's about level 8, and it was really fun too.  You give him some Honeymeads, supposed to raise faction, but I didn't get xp or faction increase.  Then you ask him 'who is Sragg'.  He takes a roundabout walk.  When he walks past the Lion's Mane into the alley attack there. (I killed him twice there)  Try to root him or have two attackers, so he doesn't run back to the bar.  Not sure what happens if the guards see you finish him off, maybe nothing.<BR>
<BR>
Also leave an open inventory slot before giving head to Byzar.  Byzar must con amiable.  Just hail him first and hand him the head.
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
