	<tr>
		
			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				To get the hammer:<BR>
1. Kill Trumpy Irontoe<BR>
(can be found in Fish's Bar near docks)<BR>
Do not try to kill him in the bar, he has 2 body<BR>
guards, and there is a bouncer.  Kill him out<BR>
on the docks as far as you can get him.<BR>
2. Take his head to Kaladim, but make sure you<BR>
con amiable to the guards (hence to Bloodforge<BR>
also) do this by killing many of the Goblins<BR>
near Kaladim. (this took me 2 hours as a Barbarian<BR>
Shaman at 9th level)<BR>
3.  Gather War beads, NOT shattered beads, you<BR>
will need 4 sets of beads to give to Bloodforge.<BR>
4.  Go to back room in Warrior's Guild (through<BR>
the dining area)in Kaladim and find Bloodforge.<BR>
5.  Hail Bloodforge, give him 4 sets of War beads<BR>
and he will acknowledge it with experiance points.<BR>
6. Give him Trumpy's head.  He will reward you<BR>
with the hammer.<BR>
<BR>
*note***  You can NOT put the head in the bank,<BR>
or give it to a friend.  If you do not give him<BR>
the war beads first and are not amiable, <BR>
you WILL NOT get a hammer from Bloodforge.
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
