				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Ok,<BR>
I did the quest, have the hammer. The quest is so highly known now, that ppl just kill trumpy and give the head to Blyzar Bloodforge and you get your hammer. Now I didn't pay attention to the con rating but I had no troubles, I am a Barb shaman. Now I would HIGHLY recommend doing the ogre head quest first, because a) It raises your faction with him and b) I got a BLACKENED IRON CROWN for turning in the 2 ogre heads. I about died... he will then ask you if you would like to do a little trip, that is where the Trumpy part comes in. Now when I did the quest, the heads were not lore, but they are now and are no drop/trade etc. as well. <BR>
The weapon lights about like a regular lightstone and does decent dmg, however even at max'ed skill in 2H Blunt I miss a lot and with 50 dly that hurts. (I missed a lotwith my lvl 25 shaman as well). SO, here is the story, plain simple, factual. So good luck on getting your blackened stuff, I got really lucky, but do teh ogre head quest..:) It may be worth your time. <BR>
